snippet.title: ZGMF-X71T Arch Destiny Gundam - THE REVEAL

localized.description:
NOTE: I am not yelling. My Voice is just Naturally Loud and I am also being VERY PASSIONATE at the same time.

THE TIME HAS FINALLY COME!

This gundam is officially ready to see the light of day, and HERE IT IS!

Feel free to give us a Full Critique on it as you see fit in the comments section.
If you're an artist who wants to make Artwork of this gundam as well, then GO AHEAD! The Door's Open! Just make sure to give credit to Me and TheAnimeOverviewer for it, that's all.

To my friend, TheAnimeOverviewer; We finally did it, dude! =D

But alas, ENJOY!!! =D

P.S. NEW BACKGROUND IMAGE! WindomXP has long since Died Out, so it's time to move onto the next big thing. Gundam Extreme VS. Maxi Boost!
